    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality find for a discerning buyer. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no chips or scratches, while the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it performs perfectly, having been meticulously maintained and garage-kept its entire life. You can expect a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership.",
