      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a project or for parts. The engine currently has significant oil leaks and the transmission shifts roughly, indicating a need for major mechanical attention. Cosmetically, the exterior has several large dents and peeling paint, while the interior shows heavy wear and tear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It is recommended that any potential buyer brings a mechanic to assess the full extent of the repairs needed.",
