    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of unparalleled distinction. This specimen has been maintained to exacting standards, remaining in showroom condition both mechanically and aesthetically. From the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, untouched interior, this motorcar offers an ownership experience indistinguishable from a new delivery. This is an acquisition intended for the discerning individual who demands nothing less than absolute perfection.",
