    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty. It's honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely spotless and drives like a total dream! I've taken such good care of it, and it really shows in every detail. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. I'd love for you to come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Offering an impeccable E92 M3, a definitive example of the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 era. This vehicle features eight individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline, delivering linear power through a lightning-quick M-DCT dual-clutch transmission. Mechanically optimized with documented rod bearing replacement and reinforced throttle actuators, the drivetrain is as robust as it is visceral. The chassis exhibits factory-spec rigidity with no subframe stress, complemented by an M-variable limited-slip differential for precise torque vectoring. Finished in original paint with a flawless interior, this collector-grade specimen represents the apex of naturally aspirated M-division engineering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
